vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Specific Use Permit for a commercial amusement (outside) use on property zoned MU-1 Mixed Use District, on the west line of Coit Road, south of McCallum Boulevard
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval for a two-year period, subject to a site/landscape plan and conditions
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval for a two-year period, subject to a site/landscape plan and conditions
Z201-333(OA)
